The scripts in this directory demonstrate the data page growing when doing multiple
consecutive INSERTS/UPDATES/DELETES into the same table.

01-install-extensions.sh 
  installs the required extension into the database

02-mvcc-test.sh          
  demonstates how the data pages react to multiple tuple updates

03-vacuum-test.sh        
  forces a vacuum on the magazine table to see how space can be manually reclaimed